<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">Dear <%= @client.name %>,</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <strong><%= @freelancer.name %></strong> has submitted the requested changes for your task, "<strong><%= @task.title %></strong>."
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;"><strong>Updated Task Details:</strong></p>
<table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse;">
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Task ID:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.id %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Title:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.title %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Description:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.description %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Budget:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= number_to_currency(@task.budget, unit: "ZMK ", format: "%u%n") %></td>
  </tr>
  <tr style="border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;">
    <th style="text-align: left; padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Deadline:</th>
    <td style="padding: 8px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><%= @task.deadline ? @task.deadline.strftime("%B %d, %Y") : "Not set" %></td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Please take a moment to review the submitted changes and provide your feedback. If you are satisfied with the updates, you can approve the task's completion directly on GigHive. Should further changes be necessary, please communicate with the freelancer through the platform.
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  You can review the task and provide feedback here:
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <%= link_to 'Review Task on GigHive', task_url(@task), style: 'color: #007BFF; text-decoration: none; display: inline-block; padding: 10px 20px; background-color: #007BFF; color: #fff; border-radius: 5px;' %>
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Thank you for collaborating with GigHive. We are committed to ensuring a smooth and successful experience for you!
</p>

<p style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  Sincerely,<br>
  The GigHive Team
</p>